Package myAdapter

Class ListAdapter

java.lang.Object
myAdapter.ListAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
HCollection, HList
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListAdapter.SubListAdapter
public class ListAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements HList
A ListAdapter implemented using a java.util.Vector as adaptee. It implements the HList interface. It allows duplicates.

  • Nested Class Summary

    Nested Classes
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ListAdapter.SubListAdapter
    A ListAdapter which derives from another ListAdapter, implemented using a java.util.Vector as adaptee.

    • ListAdapter

      public ListAdapter​(int initialCapacity)
      ListAdapter created using a java.util.Vector as adaptee. The constructor with a initial capacity as parameter instantiate a vector with a initial capacity passed when the SetAdapter is created.
      Parameters:
      initialCapacity - The initial capacity of the ListAdapter, which is equal to the initial capacity of the java.util.Vector (the adaptee) which is used.
